Theorem (invinj):
  for all v0, (if v0 is a group then for all v1, (for all v2, (if v1 is an element of v0 and v2 is an element of v0 and v1 ^{-1, v0 } is equal to v2 ^{-1, v0 } then v1 is equal to v2)))
Proof:
Qed.

